After pushing an update to Bioconductor it can take up to 48 hours for the results to propagate to the build system and appear on the package landing pages.

The building and checking of packages occurs nightly -  You pushed Yesterday evening and most likely did not make the cutoff (4:45 PM EST)  for todays build report.  Your updates should be picked up on tonight's build and be reflected in tomorrow's report.  If the build and check were successful the new package version will also be available via install after the builds complete and propagate.

Cheers,


